java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
public class InformationTableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel

This class defines the table model used for displaying some information of any CommDB database. This model is shown graphically below: | Table | Entries | Max. Entries | Schema | | | | | |
